Preconditions:
The input array `nums` must not be null.
The input array `queries` must not be null.
The length of the input array `nums` must be greater than or equal to the length of the input array `queries`.

Postconditions:
The returned array `answer` will have the same length as the input array `queries`.
Each element `answer[i]` in the returned array will be the answer to the `i-th` query.